<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7884956e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s162"><num value="162">§ 162.</num><heading> Creation of China corporations restricted</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No corporation for the purpose of engaging in business within China shall be created under any law of the United States other than this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7884956f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1922-09-19/ch346/s29">Sept. 19, 1922, ch. 346, § 29</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/act/1925-02-26/ch345/s13">Feb. 26, 1925, ch. 345, § 13</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/43/997">43 Stat. 997</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
